title: MonkaS (Rick and Morty)
body:
I am not usually surprised by networks who over promote stuff... but adult swim has put out 3,121 clips related to Rick and Morty alone.... like... that is a STAGGERING amount of videos considering the lifespan of the show.

some of them are actually really good too, here is an origins video that I really enjoyed.....
